## ğŸ“‹ About The Project

SmartFarming-Lavender-AI is an intelligent farming system that integrates **IoT sensors**, **AI models**, and **smart devices** to optimize lavender cultivation. The system monitors soil health, controls climate, detects pests, and enhances essential oil yield.

